{"tid":1630662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［眾籌做善事］我想夾錢幫下的士狗雙腳既醫藥費","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:19.000Z","uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"765a77c1f489903f2d6d2263dc985615dbcd5395","tid":1630662,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"的士狗雙腳斷晒，日後行動不便，我想幫下手，有無人跟機？"},{"pid":"53466398241f4596d4d9885d513677460b7f262e","tid":1630662,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:31.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"acc1e41d6503e6f406a2d07920a385b9f05547ff","tid":1630662,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"［最新消息］全民起動 三罷民意調查<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們暫時收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6kyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=f43c49d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a> 或掃QR code填寫問卷。<br />\n<br />\n民調將於10月11日中午12時結束。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asueaF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasueaF0.jpg&h=c85840ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0e4da05d7658175d53642c6f1880f109e393194","tid":1630662,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"唔係只係爆江咋咩？<br />\n反而手足對腳斷撚咗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf256f8c5ace68e5b4f179bc52dcd95b40b1198","tid":1630662,"uid":144592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765a77c1f489903f2d6d2263dc985615dbcd5395","tid":1630662,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"的士狗雙腳斷晒，日後行動不便，我想幫下手，有無人跟機？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"眾你老母   手足比人撞雙腳骨折"},{"pid":"671c9b851f3aa64be54f3571204f1a2a42345f30","tid":1630662,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a520e5765059c086244af3b03a8a78f6eb7c59fe","tid":1630662,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0e4da05d7658175d53642c6f1880f109e393194","tid":1630662,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"唔係只係爆江咋咩？<br />\n反而手足對腳斷撚咗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"大佬....唔駛講咁白喇...."}]}